reviews.review_text: Great sound for such a last time. A very nice recording. This sounds amazing for an audience recording.

Great show This is when the deck crashed at the campground.  I was right next to the building it was choas.  Jerry just sounds OK and the setlist didn;t make the crowd go nuts-  Take me to the River- Riverfront arena,  Big Boss man etc.  I can clearly remember this show, the twirling bunch stage right.   any hoo I really miss it but all good things etc.  Bluegrass festivals are now rockin and Leftover Salmon filled a void there  love them

Pretty good for '95 Sounds amazing for an audience recording, and the band actually delivers on this one (well for '95 that it.)  20 min Eyes??  That's gotta be the longest of the year.  4 Stars for the recording and the Eyes, would be a 5 but it's '95.
